    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在印度神话永恒的怀抱中，两颗灵魂相融时比分离更耀眼。欢迎来到TWIN FLAMES，一款回合制合作解谜冒险游戏，你将引导传奇恋人Savitri和Satyavan开启第27次不灭统一的征程。探索生动低多边形世界，充斥古老奇观——从茂密 enchanted 森林到星辰点缀的天空虚空——破解复杂六边形谜题，追求完美和谐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/0ae42986b19ff6cad836f73b04f0fd77.poster.avif?t=1768974995\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/0ae42986b19ff6cad836f73b04f0fd77.webm?t=1768974995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/0ae42986b19ff6cad836f73b04f0fd77.mp4?t=1768974995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人模式下化身为双重火焰，舞动命运之舞，或邀请伙伴共赴本地合作激情，每一次同步行动都深化你们的联结，揭开感人叙事。智斗环境险阻，调和宇宙能量，挑战诸神本身——这些考验融合巧妙策略与情感深度。这一循环中，爱能否征服命运？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >源自献身与重生的史诗传说，<strong>TWIN FLAMES</strong>捕捉共享旅程的魔力。以色彩与宁静爆发的极简艺术、直观操控，以及从微弱火花演变为熊熊烈焰的谜题，它是解谜爱好者、神话迷，以及所有寻求温暖灵魂故事玩家的浪漫史诗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/2fc1be9106835b7effe3e7a7f6368fcd.poster.avif?t=1768974995\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/2fc1be9106835b7effe3e7a7f6368fcd.webm?t=1768974995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/2fc1be9106835b7effe3e7a7f6368fcd.mp4?t=1768974995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>灵魂联结谜题：</strong> 挑战回合制六边形谜局，奖励逻辑、时机与团队协作——从新手火焰进化为永恒大师。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作或单人火焰：</strong> 无缝切换单人单控至本地合作双控，双倍激情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神话浪漫：</strong> 沉浸于Savitri传奇誓言编织的叙事，探索爱、失落与重生主题，跨越50+手工关卡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>惊艳低多边形美学：</strong> 穿越多彩绝美王国，融合宁静之美与超凡神秘——每个世界独一无二。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松却丰盈：</strong> 短时局适合浪漫之夜或独处冥想，成就系统庆祝你们日益深厚的羁绊。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/02123f1dcd23edd7db4d707dd644df0a.poster.avif?t=1768974995\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/02123f1dcd23edd7db4d707dd644df0a.webm?t=1768974995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084560/extras/02123f1dcd23edd7db4d707dd644df0a.mp4?t=1768974995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备点燃火焰？TWIN FLAMES即将登陆——立即加入愿望单，让命运召唤！</h2>",
